WEBVTT

00:00:00.960 --> 00:00:05.496
I'm here today to talk to you
about a very powerful little word,

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:08.055
one that people will do almost anything

00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:09.360
to avoid becoming.

00:00:10.280 --> 00:00:12.536
Billion-dollar industries thrive

00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:14.336
because of the fear of it,

00:00:14.360 --> 00:00:17.536
and those of us who undeniably are it

00:00:17.560 --> 00:00:19.896
are left to navigate a relentless storm

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:21.120
surrounding it.

00:00:22.120 --> 00:00:24.856
I'm not sure if any of you have noticed,

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:26.240
but I'm fat.

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:30.576
Not the lowercase,
muttered-behind-my-back kind,